                <head>Comments</head>
                <p xml:id="KR5f0021-start">
                    <seg corresp="#KR5f0021_tls_001-200a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-06-08T17:17:19.931+09:00">Han Fei was hoping to make political contributions</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5f0021_tls_001-200a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-06-08T17:17:48.899+09:00">but Li Si caused his death.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5f0021_tls_001-589a.42" xml:lang="en" resp="#paulfahr" modified="2024-07-05T06:06:17.497+09:00">If somebody faces death, but manages to survive</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5f0021_tls_001-589a.43" xml:lang="en" resp="#paulfahr" modified="2024-07-05T06:06:32.655+09:00">he will be immensely happy.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5f0021_tls_001-589a.44" xml:lang="en" resp="#paulfahr" modified="2024-07-05T06:07:05.647+09:00">[If this is the case,] it would be better if he had never faced death in the first place.</seg>
                </p>
